library(prophet)
## Loading required package: Rcpp
## Loading required package: rlang
slinky_dog <- read.csv("~/Downloads/Disney Data/park_data/Hollywood_Studios/slinky_dog.csv")

colnames(slinky_dog)[colnames(slinky_dog) == 'datetime'] <- 'ds'
colnames(slinky_dog)[colnames(slinky_dog) == 'SPOSTMIN'] <- 'y'

slinky_dog <- slinky_dog[slinky_dog$y >= 0, ]

m <- prophet(slinky_dog, changepoint.prior.scale=0.01)

future <- make_future_dataframe(m, periods = 300, freq = 60 * 60)

fcst <- predict(m, future)
plot(m, fcst)

prophet_plot_components(m, fcst)
